00:41:13.000 --> 00:41:15.541
But you just have to work with
what you're handed, basically.

00:41:15.541 --> 00:41:18.459
So it's kind of like Clue
where you hand out the-- you

00:41:18.459 --> 00:41:20.500
have whatever evidence
you have in the beginning.

00:41:20.500 --> 00:41:22.355
So that's another one
that I think is fun.

00:41:22.355 --> 00:41:23.570
It's good with kids, too.

